Error 1227 (42000): Access denied; you need (at least one of) the CREATE USER privilege(s) for this operation
set password = 's2' retain current password;
Error 1227 (42000): Access denied; you need (at least one of) the CREATE USER or APPLICATION_PASSWORD_ADMIN privilege(s) for this operation
grant application_password_admin on *.* to dpself;
set password = 's2' retain current password;
revoke application_password_admin on *.* from dpself;
alter user 'dpself'@'%' discard old password;
